4.22	Ma'on,_Har_Hebron	Ma'on, Har Hebron	Ma'on (Hebrew: ‎‎) is an Israeli settlement and a moshav shitufi in the Judean Hills of the West Bank, located south of Hebron and north of Beersheba. It is part of the Har Hebron Regional Council. The international community considers Israeli settlements in the West Bank illegal under international law, but the Israeli government disputes this.	http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/6/62/Maon_1.JPG/300px-Maon_1.JPG
